		"Name": "Daikyu",
		"Details": "Named for an anicent Japanese longbow and first produced in 3055, the Daikyu is armed for long-range combat. The design has a high ground speed for its weight, allowing it to dictate the range it engages the enemy at and keeps it in optimal range for its guns. The Daikyu DAI-03 is a fast brawler model and uses a 350-rated Light Fusion Engine for power while Endo-Steel and Ferro-Fibrous construction materials provide free weight. A MASC system boosts the already impressive ground speed and lets the DAI-03 bring its ER PPC, ER Medium Laser, and MRM-20 to bear very quickly. A C3 Slave keeps the Daikyu connected to allied targeting information.",
		"Icon": "uixTxrIcon_daikyu"
